    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְעוֹבִי הַלְּבִזְבְּזִין נִמְדָּד, וּבֵינֵיהֶן אֵין נִמְדָּד. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2920\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון שזורי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-47684\">רַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span>",
