    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵימָא: <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2920\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון שזורי\">רַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן שֵׁזוּרִי</span> אוֹמֵר: יָיִן. <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"74\" data-sentence-id=\"3\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תַּנְיָא, אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2920\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון שזורי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-47686\">רַבִּי</span>",
