      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Ravin bar Ḥinnana, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"149\" data-full-name=\"Ravin bar Ḥinnana\" data-name-he=\"רבין בר חיננא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-47690\">בַּר חִינָּנָא</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Ulla, second and third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2409\" data-full-name=\"Ulla\" data-name-he=\"עולא נחותא\">עוּלָּא</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Ḥanina bar Ḥama II, first-generation I Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1212\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Ḥanina bar Ḥama II\" data-name-he=\"רבי חנינא בר חמא\">רַבִּי חֲנִינָא</span>: הֲלָכָה <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2920\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Shezuri\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון שזורי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-47693\">כְּרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
